---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import { t } from '@/i18n/store';
---

<Layout title="Horoscop Zilnic - Astro Mystical">
  <Header />
  
  <div class="min-h-screen py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-mystical-50 mb-4">Horoscop Zilnic</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mystical-300">Ghidarea ta cosmică personalizată pentru azi</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Horoscope Card -->
      <div class="bg-mystical-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-mystical-700 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cosmic-500 to-spiritual-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="Star" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-mystical-50">Aries</h2>
              <p class="text-mystical-300">March 21 - April 19</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
              <p class="text-mystical-400 text-sm">Data de azi</p>
              <p class="text-mystical-200 font-medium">19 Decembrie 2024</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Main Reading -->
          <div class="bg-mystical-900/50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-mystical-50 mb-3 flex items-center">
              <Icon name="Zap" class="w-5 h-5 text-cosmic-400 mr-2" />
              Mesajul Cosmic de Azi
            </h3>
            <p class="text-mystical-300 leading-relaxed">
              Stelele se aliniază în favoarea ta astăzi, dragă Berbec. Calitățile tale naturale de lider sunt amplificate,
              iar universul îți trimite semnale clare să acționezi cu îndrăzneală. Ai încredere în instinctele tale și nu
              te teme să ieși în evidență. Ideile tale inovatoare vor fi bine primite de cei din jur.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Lucky Elements -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-mystical-900/50 rounded-xl p-4">
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-mystical-50 mb-2 flex items-center">
                <Icon name="Star" class="w-4 h-4 text-cosmic-400 mr-2" />
                Numere Norocoase
              </h4>
              <div class="flex space-x-2">
                <span class="bg-cosmic-500/20 text-cosmic-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">7</span>
                <span class="bg-cosmic-500/20 text-cosmic-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">14</span>
                <span class="bg-cosmic-500/20 text-cosmic-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">21</span>
                <span class="bg-cosmic-500/20 text-cosmic-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">28</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-mystical-900/50 rounded-xl p-4">
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-mystical-50 mb-2 flex items-center">
                <Icon name="Heart" class="w-4 h-4 text-spiritual-400 mr-2" />
                Culori Norocoase
              </h4>
              <div class="flex space-x-2">
                <span class="bg-red-500/20 text-red-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Red</span>
                <span class="bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Orange</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-mystical-900/50 rounded-xl p-4">
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-mystical-50 mb-2 flex items-center">
                <Icon name="Moon" class="w-4 h-4 text-cosmic-400 mr-2" />
                Dispoziție
              </h4>
              <span class="bg-cosmic-500/20 text-cosmic-300 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Încrezător & Energetic</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Compatibility -->
          <div class="bg-mystical-900/50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-mystical-50 mb-3">Compatibilitatea de Azi</h3>
            <p class="text-mystical-300 mb-4">
              Energia ta rezonează puternic cu Leu și Săgetător astăzi. Aceste semne de foc îți vor
              înțelege nevoia de aventură și entuziasm.
            </p>
            <div class="flex space-x-4">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold">♌</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-mystical-300">Leo</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-cosmic-400">95%</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold">♐</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-mystical-300">Sagittarius</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-cosmic-400">92%</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Action Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cosmic-500 to-spiritual-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:from-cosmic-600 hover:to-spiritual-600 transition-all duration-300">Citire Detaliată</button>
        <button class="border border-cosmic-500 text-cosmic-400 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-cosmic-500/10 transition-all duration-300">Distribuie prietenilor</button>
        <button class="border border-spiritual-500 text-spiritual-400 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-spiritual-500/10 transition-all duration-300">Salvează în jurnal</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Layout>



